-- Yen Near Seven-Month High Against Dollar on Concern Global Economy Slowing
-- Ron Harui
-- 2010-07-02T00:36:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/yen-near-seven-month-high-against-dollar-on-concern-global-economy-slowing.html

          
          
             The dollar dropped to an eight-week
low versus the pound on speculation the U.S. economic recovery
is slowing.  
 The U.S. currency fell to $1.5194 per pound as of 9:34 a.m.
in Tokyo from $1.5177 in New York yesterday. It earlier declined
to $1.5198, the weakest since May 4.  
